{"tid":1104680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★突發！派$4000收270萬份申請　暫1.4萬人獲發全額","createTime":"2019-04-13T10:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T08:08:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"27211925136de2448a95c894a0c2eaf9da9c62b3","tid":1104680,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T10:02:53.000Z","msg":"270萬香港人近日等緊一封信，究竟是甚麼信件？答案自然是4000港元關愛共享計劃的申請結果通知書。有市民今日(13日)在社交網站Facebook上載該封信件，指可收足4000港元，並於7天內過數予其銀行戶口。信件簽發日期是本周二(9日)，亦即在職家庭津貼辦事處首日發放4000港元的日子。換言之，該名網民是首批收錢的幸運兒。<br />\n<br />\n職津處回覆東網指，由本周二至昨日(12日)，已就約2萬宗成功申請個案指示銀行發放款項，當中，約70%獲全數4000港元，即約1.4萬人。截至本周四(11日)，職津處共收到逾270萬份申請，已向約170萬申請人發出申請確認通知。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190413/bkn-20190413153002524-0413_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190413%2Fbkn-20190413153002524-0413_00822_001.html&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=9a5ab04e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190413/bkn-20190413153002524-0413_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"96eab3d23d3292a1427b15c01383ef7447d359d2","tid":1104680,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":28,"score":-25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T10:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190413/photo/bkn-20190413153002524-0413_00822_001_02b.jpg?20190413180039\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190413%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190413153002524-0413_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20190413180039&h=4648adae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5da1138e68e4195d59529ece82bbbc4ea887fdab","tid":1104680,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":35,"score":-34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T10:04:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190413/photo/bkn-20190413153002524-0413_00822_001_01b.jpg?20190413180039\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fne